    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant investment to become roadworthy again. The engine has major mechanical issues, including a failed head gasket and a transmission that slips badly in higher gears. Externally, the body shows heavy rust along the rocker panels and several large dents on the rear passenger side. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This car is ideal for a mechanic looking for a donor vehicle or a dedicated hobbyist ready for a complete restoration project.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
