    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a comprehensive professional inspection, confirming that all mechanical systems operate with precision and consistency. The exterior and interior finishes remain in commendable states, reflecting a history of responsible ownership and attentive care. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a dependable asset that delivers both comfort and longevity.",
      "price": 29950.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
