    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver without the 'new car' price tag. Everything runs smoothly, and it's ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great home!",
